{"tid":1248480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[[提防]] 前功盡廢撚，攞彩撚同埋見好就收撚","createTime":"2019-06-21T12:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T09:18:35.000Z","uid":203889,"like":54,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a69d45bf02b52e42baeedaf833394f8dacce51b0","tid":1248480,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"小心，有班人懶係苦口婆心咁叫人唔好出黎<br />\n1.叫人收手，如果唔係前功盡廢<br />\n2.你地都攞晒彩啦<br />\n3. 見好就收啦<br />\n<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求一樣都未兌現！</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 完全撤回《逃犯條例》修訂<br />\n2. 完全收回對 612 衝突的「暴動定性」<br />\n3. 撤控並釋放全數被捕示威者<br />\n4. 追究警方濫暴濫權<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">（而家要追究埋醫院）</span><br />\n5. 林鄭下台<br />\n<br />\n大家小心！！未完！！！！"},{"pid":"7a626ec0adf02b041bb7fd208855ac26b6077ac1","tid":1248480,"uid":203889,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:57:59.000Z","msg":"提防！<br />\n元秋都爆左響口，件事未完！！！"},{"pid":"474fe2031ea0723b3a9bffc86cd28207180c0085","tid":1248480,"uid":2612,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必睇!!!!!<br />\n認真, 咁多位義士<br />\n呢個係狗屋( 警察總部)<br />\n入面無野多, 狗最多, 軍火最多<br />\n再者軍火多, 你衝入去可以認為你想搶槍<br />\n實彈射擊你班友, 我唔想每年平反621<br />\n衝就一定, 但唔係狗屋<br />\n認清目標, 叫親你衝狗屋既, 一係三毛, 一係警犬, 一係有病<br />\n圍住, 守住狗屋就好足夠<br />\n唔好受任何網上/現場既人挑釁<br />\n你要守, 要挨<br />\n衝立會係唔比開會, 衝狗屋係無撚用, 佢地出唔到黎就得<br />\n有傳 狗已部署重兵4千, 前後夾擊, 一擊就夾死你地!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190621&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59743894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190621%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59743894&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDclcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=ba26861d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190621%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59743894&h=09f88b5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=2019